com.jacob.jacobgen
Class Jacobgen

java.lang.Object
  com.jacob.jacobgen.Jacobgen

public class Jacobgen
extends Object

This is the root class for Jacobgen. It generates Jacob wrapper class for windows DLLs. Run this class with no command line parameters to get a list of the valid command line options %JRE% -Xint com.jacob.jacobgen.Jacobgen %1 %2 %3 %4 %5

Version:
$Id$
Author:
Massimiliano Bigatti
